ing without results. The outcomes of their philosophies and funding tell a different story:  capitalism weakened, democratic republics destabilized, sovereignty eroded, and movements with Marxist agendas bankrolled globally.  From U.S. prosecutors who cripple law enforcement, to radical protest networks like Indivisible and No Kings, to political engineering in Burma through the National Unity Government (NUG)\u2014the pattern is unmistakable. ", "large_image": "NE9mss60D5146CQy.png", "title": "The Open Society Illusion: How George Soros and Karl Popper Undermined Capitalism, Funded Marxist Agendas, and Destabilized Nations"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBvLsTCP", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 34, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8735295, "raw_content": "This practice allowed them to fire Americans who were creative and innovators, and hired and trained cheap Indians to do the work.\n\nThey have eliminated traditional R&D, and replaced it with stealing and building good enough products. Unfortunately for them, it is not good enough for AI and now those companies have a bunch of Indians who can't deliver on new AI innovations, especially on data development, hence why China has overtaken America in AI. China doesn't use Indians while America does.", "author": "Tomis_4", "created": 1784386374960, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "residue69", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\u200bIndians are fucking up big tech companies as customers are protecting their innovation and, frankly, Indians aren't creative. MSFT, IBM, META are notorious for monitoring what their customers are doing with their products and stealing ideas and creating new products.", "last_comment_created": 1784396048777, "content": "<p>This practice allowed them to fire Americans who were creative and innovators, and hired and trained cheap Indians to do the work.</p>\n<p>They have eliminated traditional R&amp;D, and replaced it with stealing and building good enough products. Unfortunately for them, it is not good enough for AI and now those companies have a bunch of Indians who can't deliver on new AI innovations, especially on data development, hence why China has overtaken America in AI. China doesn't use Indians while America does.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 34, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBvLtZKP", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 15, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8735685, "raw_content": "", "author": "Parabelum", "created": 1784403643395, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Yemen", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBvLtZKP.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/oPvsJXk0FmTY.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/0Xqp5Bx0tL35a8ET.png", "width": 741, "content-type": "png", "height": 762}], "blurhash": "U1S6Pl00_3D%9Fayt7t7_3t7WBRjxuj[ofRj", "full_resolution": [762, 741]}, "title": "My position on Flock - I expect nobody will read it because